      "content": "i've tried everything. the meds, the doctors, the physical therapy... nothing works. it's not even about \"managing\" it anymore, it's just about existing through the torture. sometimes i just lie here thinking how much easier it would be if i just didn't have to wake up to this anymore. if things could just be still for once.",
